{"title":"What film or literature is useful for making sense of the AI moment?","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/897901412/0/marginalrevolution~What-film-or-literature-is-useful-for-making-sense-of-the-AI-moment.html","date":1716964980000,"content":"<p>That is a reader query, I take it there is no point in my trotting through the obvious picks, starting with <em>I, Robot</em> and <em>Her</em>.  Sophisticates will ponder Stanislaw Lem’s <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Cyberiad-Fables-Cybernetic-Penguin-Classics/dp/0141394595/ref=sr_1_1?crid=2WM5XSVUT5PYQ&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.QTIemsWC12yV5VFy0miXqjs84fwpmzcrU9r3xKpV-diV7u8562k_ONTe5PZG7f5B_RunLBwghvrppN-Q5cnW6B_nc2SjICStJxf9_UNtlI5uR0wg6uZRZ6fnUO_oqXTlK0jcgNEQP5-WvKuq4QgbGieoHsj9Iemp4deMrGXzI0fRXk2FmcnZfIojelB1fqKrE8Xb22A7U6ItMu6wvSHG_535tzA30znV9wgt59p7Zq0.LR5GbbABzamHYBo774bOOYAb5dzT9JtbLbqwuokFq3o&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=stanislaw+lem+cyberiad&amp;qid=1716817308&amp;sprefix=stanislaw+lem+c%2Caps%2C154&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">Cyberiad</a>, which very well understood the quirky and semi-religious potential in LLMs, even though he was writing in Communist Poland a very long time ago (those people loved to talk about cybernetics).</p>\r\n<p>Have you ever pondered the 1994 Sandra Bullock movie <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speed_(1994_film)\" target=\"_blank\">Speed</a>?  I think at this point it is not a spoiler to report “It revolves around a bus that is rigged by an extortionist to explode if its <em>speed</em> falls below 50 miles per hour.”  And yes, this is a Hollywood movie of the 1990s, so it does end in a kiss.</p>\r\n<p>Here is <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://twitter.com/krishnanrohit/status/1770012082190389602?s=48&amp;t=gefmhscjm4RmSTlElCt5Qw\" target=\"_blank\">a visual mapping of how science fiction has made sense of AI.</a>  Am I neglecting any other non-obvious picks?</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/05/what-film-or-literature-is-useful-for-making-sense-of-the-ai-moment.html\">What film or literature is useful for making sense of the AI moment?</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/897901412/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/897901412/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/897901412/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/897901412/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/897901412/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/897901412/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/rss20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/05/what-film-or-literature-is-useful-for-making-sense-of-the-ai-moment.html#comments\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/comments20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/05/what-film-or-literature-is-useful-for-making-sense-of-the-ai-moment.html/feed\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/commentsrss20.png\" /></a> \r\n<div><a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/05/what-film-or-literature-is-useful-for-making-sense-of-the-ai-moment.html#comments\"><h3>Comments</h3></a><ul><li